# v2.8.8 - 2026-06-26

## Improvements:
- Improve robustness of CSV import by guessing encoding (PL-3114).
- Enhance style for dashed resolution lines (PL-3167).
- Update Pore Network Model (PNM) default values in FixedRadius and Two-phase simulations (PL-3167).
- Set Equal Angles and Constant Difference as default models (PL-3167).

## Bug fixes:
- Address a bug affecting Krel results.
- Fix corruption of Krel results during save/load operations (PL-3168).
- Resolve issues in MICP, One-phase, and other sub-resolution model simulations (PL-3168).
- Correct CDF attribution in MICP, `throat.volume` calculations in Kabs and MICP, and Kabs REV parameters (PL-3179).
- Resolve `NoneType` attribute errors during PNM simulation (PL-3151).
- Fix issues with network connection calculations (PL-3171).
- Restore the "Apply" button functionality on the PNM Simulation widget (PL-3167).
- Correct chart unit behavior at startup (PL-3167).
- Ensure the conversion factor is correctly applied (PL-3167).

